Now let's set the crontab to make your PC or server execute the python document everyday~
First you should create a crontab document just like "vim test.cron";
Then you could use "crontab -e" to set your wanted time to receive your email;
Next write the test.cron to your log;
Check the current crontab, crontab -l,make sure your task is written in the system;
Finally, check your email!
